description: The Woodees VoIP adapter allows you to talk to your friends and family for free (via a VoIP program) while using your favorite headset with microphone. Simply connect the adapter to your computer headphone and microphone jacks and then attach your headset with microphone (3.5mm) and you are ready to go! Do you need a way to reduce how much you pack for business trips. The Woodees VoIP adapter allows you to utilize your smartphone headset with your laptop and use your internet chat, voice recognition, and gaming softwares. You no longer need to pack two headsets!
title: Woodees VOIPAD35 Laptop Adaptor
